<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200809/dfa006360e1243f28f1144129358b4f3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">《声入人心》今年终于有好事发生了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200809/77f124332e464e9db04c51635fb3a137.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">余迪老师和爱人陈辰迎来了他们的爱情结晶，小公主一位。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200809/23b6bbe74b66405aa2e5c14408241876.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
